Text: Ja maar ek moet dit nog rip en upload

Being in the US, bandwidth is not an issue for me. I'll be seeding all of your movies and series for quite a while.
Now if only I could find the "You Must Be Joking" movies. :(
And all of the "Oh Schucks" ones, if anybody has them.
